<前言><![CDATA[]]></前言>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These standards are enacted in accordance with Article 24 of the Refrigeration and Air Conditioning Industries Governance Act.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[A refrigeration and air conditioning enterprise shall pay a review fee of NT$500 to request the central competent authority to process any of the following applications:
1. Application for a permit.
2. Application for issuance, alteration or replacement of a refrigeration and air conditioning enterprise registration certificate.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[A refrigeration and air conditioning enterprise shall pay a certificate fee of NT$2,500 to the central competent authority for its application for issuance, alteration, replacement or reissuance of a refrigeration and air conditioning enterprise registration certificate.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These standards shall come into force from the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
</法規>
